"The purpose of the spiritual realm has never been to say how, but why. "It doesn't even do that very well.  'Why' is what drives scientists as much as how.  Trying to figure out why things are the way they are is at the heart of scientific inquiry.  The spiritual realm is not about discovering why but about telling you why.